msgid "Enable notifications and payment options"
msgstr "Luba teavitused ja maksevõimalused"

#: inc/lib/getting-started/classes/class-gs-helper.php:305
msgid "Embed the booking form using shortcode or block"
msgstr "Sisesta broneerimisvorm kasutades lühikoodi või plokki"

#: inc/lib/getting-started/classes/class-gs-helper.php:315
msgid "Add Your First Booking Form"
msgstr "Lisa oma esimene broneerimisvorm"

#: inc/lib/getting-started/classes/class-gs-helper.php:340
msgid "Add Engaging Videos — Presto Player"
msgstr "Lisa kaasahaaravaid videoid — Presto Player"

#: inc/lib/getting-started/classes/class-gs-helper.php:345
msgid ""
"Embed videos with modern features like chapters, overlays, and custom branding and keep people watching and make your "
"content unforgettable."
msgstr ""
"Sisesta videoid kaasaegsete funktsioonidega nagu peatükid, ülekatteid ja kohandatud brändingut, et hoida inimesi "
"vaatamas ja muuta sinu sisu unustamatuks."

#: inc/lib/getting-started/classes/class-gs-helper.php:352
msgid "Click “+” on any page → add Presto Player block"
msgstr "Klõpsa “+” mis tahes lehel → lisa Presto Player plokk"

#: inc/lib/getting-started/classes/class-gs-helper.php:353
msgid "Paste your video URL"
msgstr "Kleebi oma video URL"

#: inc/lib/getting-started/classes/class-gs-helper.php:354
msgid "Customize settings and click “Publish”"
msgstr "Kohanda seadeid ja klõpsa “Avalda”"

#: inc/lib/getting-started/classes/class-gs-helper.php:364
msgid "Embed Your First Video"
msgstr "Sisesta oma esimene video"

#: inc/lib/getting-started/classes/class-gs-helper.php:389
msgid "Automate Your Work — OttoKit"
msgstr "Automatiseeri oma töö — OttoKit"

#: inc/lib/getting-started/classes/class-gs-helper.php:394
msgid ""
"Connect plugins and automate routine tasks like follow-ups or form triggers without code. Let’s save you hours and keep "
"your website running on autopilot."
msgstr ""
"Ühenda pluginad ja automatiseeri rutiinsed ülesanded nagu järeltegevused või vormi käivitajad ilma koodita. Säästame "
"sulle tunde ja hoiame sinu veebisaiti automaatselt töötamas."

#: inc/lib/getting-started/classes/class-gs-helper.php:401
msgid "Sign up or log in to your OttoKit account"
msgstr "Registreeru või logi sisse oma OttoKit kontole"

#: inc/lib/getting-started/classes/class-gs-helper.php:402
msgid "Click “Create New Workflow”"
msgstr "Klõpsa “Loo uus töövoog”"

#: inc/lib/getting-started/classes/class-gs-helper.php:403
msgid "Choose a Trigger and add one or more Actions"
msgstr "Vali käivitaja ja lisa üks või mitu tegevust"

#: inc/lib/getting-started/classes/class-gs-helper.php:413
msgid "Automate Your First Task"
msgstr "Automatiseeri oma esimene ülesanne"

#: inc/lib/getting-started/classes/class-gs-helper.php:438
msgid "Start Sending Emails Reliably — SureMail"
msgstr "Alusta e-kirjade usaldusväärset saatmist — SureMail"

#: inc/lib/getting-started/classes/class-gs-helper.php:443
msgid ""
"Ensure your contact forms, order updates, and notifications actually reach inboxes. Let’s make sure your emails never "
"get lost again."
msgstr ""
"Veendu, et sinu kontaktvormid, tellimuse uuendused ja teavitused jõuavad tegelikult postkastidesse. Tagame, et sinu "
"e-kirjad ei lähe enam kunagi kaduma."

#: inc/lib/getting-started/classes/class-gs-helper.php:450
msgid "Go to Settings → SureMail → Connections"
msgstr "Mine Seaded → SureMail → Ühendused"

#: inc/lib/getting-started/classes/class-gs-helper.php:451
msgid "Click Add Connection and fill in the required email details"
msgstr "Klõpsa Lisa ühendus ja täida vajalikud e-posti andmed"

#: inc/lib/getting-started/classes/class-gs-helper.php:452
msgid "Use Send Test Mail to verify your connection is working"
msgstr "Kasuta Saada testmeil, et kontrollida, kas sinu ühendus töötab"

#: inc/lib/getting-started/classes/class-gs-helper.php:462
msgid "Send Your First Email"
msgstr "Saada oma esimene e-kiri"

#: inc/lib/getting-started/classes/class-gs-helper.php:486
msgid "Final Step Before Website Launch: Checklist"
msgstr "Viimane samm enne veebisaidi käivitamist: Kontrollnimekiri"

#: inc/lib/getting-started/classes/class-gs-helper.php:491
msgid "Launching soon?"
msgstr "Kas käivitamine on peagi?"

#: inc/lib/getting-started/classes/class-gs-helper.php:497
msgid ""
"Make sure your site is ready to go with this essential checklist. This final step will help you launch your website "
"with confidence, not chaos."
msgstr ""
"Veendu, et sinu sait on valmis minema selle olulise kontrollnimekirjaga. See viimane samm aitab sul käivitada oma "
"veebisaiti enesekindlalt, mitte kaootiliselt."

